@bryanvang 
I do agree with you, however, we are looking at a story that has been retold a million times over the last 25 years, and it is a story that I don't find very appealing. Case and point, if the creators can't even think of anything better for a maincharacter then a teenager with spiky hair, a big sword who has to fight an evil empire, then I lose interest.
Look, I'm open to it being good, but it is easier to say that is is going to be bad beforehand then being disappointed later.
